title: 5. When Does Technology Go Too Far In Business And Life?
itunes:title: 5. When Does Technology Go Too Far In Business And Life?
description:
Let's be real: the rise in technology might be good for efficiency ... but how does automation & artificial intelligence negatively affect us humans, including those crazy fucks who want to dress up as animals & comic book characters?

Also on this episode: Sal imagines himself as a panda, Vaughn hits 69 in his mini-van ... and my dad & I debunk myths about success.
